# --- Project-specific ---
# Ignore everything under data/ except the bundled sample dataset that
# the pipeline's end-to-end test depends on. (Note: must be `data/*`,
# not `data/` — git can't re-include files inside a fully-ignored dir.)
data/*
!data/sample_us_unclaimed.csv
downloads/
*.log
logs/
